    List all Transcriptome Indices. These are a special type of process result, necessary for processing other SRA samples.

    rb_transcriptome_indices_list.Rd

    List all Transcriptome Indices. These are a special type of process result, necessary for processing other SRA samples.

    Usage

    rb_transcriptome_indices_list(
  salmon_version = NULL,
  index_type = NULL,
  ordering = NULL,
  limit = NULL,
  offset = NULL,
  organism__name = NULL,
  length = NULL
)

    Arguments

    salmon_version

    string Eg. salmon 0.13.1

    index_type

    string Eg. TRANSCRIPTOME_LONG

    ordering

    string Which field to use when ordering the results.

    limit

    integer Number of results to return per page.

    offset

    integer The initial index from which to return the results.

    organism__name

    string Organism name. Eg. MUS_MUSCULUS

    length

    string Short hand for index_type Eg. short or long

    See also

    Other transcriptome_indices: rb_transcriptome_indices_read()
